casebody.data:
The People of the State of New York, Respondent-Appellant, v. James Teams, Appellant-Respondent. Submitted July 9, 1964; decided July 10, 1964. *944Edward S. Silver, District Attorney (Frank Di Lalla of counsel), for motion.

No one opposed.

Motion denied upon the ground that the order is not appeal-able to the Court of Appeals (People v. Cioffi, 1 N Y 2d 70).

Appeals dismissed upon the court’s own motion.
